        "| 2 | Exploratory Data Analysis for Time Series | [Read](chapters/chapter-02-exploratory-data-analysis.qmd) | [Open in Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/github/wanghemath/Book-MachineLearning2sda/blob/main/labs/chapter-02-exploratory-data-analysis-lab.ipynb) |\n",
