        "| 5 | Difference Equations and Dynamic Behavior | [Read](chapters/chapter-05-difference-equations-dynamic-behavior.qmd) | [Open in Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/github/wanghemath/Book-MachineLearning2sda/blob/main/labs/chapter-05-difference-equations-dynamic-behavior-lab.ipynb) |\n",
        "| 6 | Forecasting Theory and Best Linear Prediction | [Read](chapters/chapter-06-forecasting-best-linear-prediction.qmd) | [Open in Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/github/wanghemath/Book-MachineLearning2sda/blob/main/labs/chapter-06-forecasting-best-linear-prediction-lab.ipynb) |\n",
